<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Facture - {{ site.name }}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'DejaVu Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .container {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        
        /* Header */
        .header {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #f97316;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .logo-section {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 50%;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #f97316;
        }
        
        .logo span {
            color: #1e293b;
        }
        
        .company-info {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 50%;
            text-align: right;
            vertical-align: top;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        
        /* Invoice Info */
        .invoice-info {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .invoice-details {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 50%;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        
        .client-details {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 50%;
            text-align: right;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        
        .invoice-number {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .label {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }
        
        .value {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .client-box {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        .client-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        /* Table */
        .table-section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        
        th {
            background: #1e293b;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 10px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        th:last-child {
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        td {
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        td:last-child {
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        tr:nth-child(even) {
            background: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        .agent-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e293b;
        }
        
        .hours-detail {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        
        /* Totals */
        .totals-section {
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        .totals-spacer {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 60%;
        }
        
        .totals-box {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 40%;
        }
        
        .total-row {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .total-label {
            display: table-cell;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        
        .total-value {
            display: table-cell;
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .grand-total {
            background: #f97316;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        
        .grand-total .total-label,
        .grand-total .total-value {
            color: white;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            text-align: center;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer-note {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        /* Summary Stats */
        .stats-row {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .stat-box {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 25%;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #f8fafc;
            text-align: center;
            border-right: 3px solid white;
        }
        
        .stat-box:last-child {
            border-right: none;
        }
        
        .stat-value {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #f97316;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #64748b;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        /* Badge */
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 3px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .badge-success {
            background: #dcfce7;
            color: #15803d;
        }
        
        .badge-danger {
            background: #fee2e2;
            color: #dc2626;
        }
        
        .badge-secondary {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            color: #64748b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo-section">
                <div class="logo">Phoenix<span>Security</span></div>
                <p style="color: #64748b; margin-top: 5px;">Services de sécurité privée</p>
            </div>
            <div class="company-info">
                <strong>Phoenix Security SARL</strong><br>
                123 Avenue de la Sécurité<br>
                75001 Paris, France<br>
                Tél: 01 23 45 67 89<br>
                contact@phoenix-security.fr
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Invoice Info -->
        <div class="invoice-info">
            <div class="invoice-details">
                <div class="invoice-number">FACTURE #{{ invoiceNumber }}</div>
                <div class="label">Date d'émission</div>
                <div class="value">{{ invoiceDate|date('d/m/Y') }}</div>
                <div class="label">Période de facturation</div>
                <div class="value">{{ periodLabel }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="client-details">
                <div class="client-box">
                    <div class="label">Facturé à</div>
                    <div class="client-name">{{ site.name }}</div>
                    <div>{{ site.address }}</div>
                    {% if site.city %}
                        <div>{{ site.city }}</div>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% if site.contactName %}
                        <div style="margin-top: 5px;">Contact: {{ site.contactName }}</div>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% if site.contactPhone %}
                        <div>Tél: {{ site.contactPhone }}</div>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Stats Summary -->
        <div class="stats-row">
            <div class="stat-box">
                <div class="stat-value">{{ totalShifts }}</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Interventions</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
                <div class="stat-value">{{ totalHoursDay|number_format(1) }}h</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Heures jour</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
                <div class="stat-value">{{ totalHoursNight|number_format(1) }}h</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Heures nuit</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
                <div class="stat-value">{{ totalHours|number_format(1) }}h</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Total heures</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Agents Table -->
        <div class="table-section">
            <div class="section-title">Détail par Agent</div>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Agent</th>
                        <th>Interventions</th>
                        <th>H. Jour</th>
                        <th>H. Nuit</th>
                        <th>Total</th>
                        <th>Montant HT</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% set subtotal = 0 %}
                    {% for data in agentsData %}
                        {% set agentAmount = (data.hours_day * hourlyRateDay) + (data.hours_night * hourlyRateNight) %}
                        {% set subtotal = subtotal + agentAmount %}
                        <tr>
                            <td class="agent-name">{{ data.agent.firstName }} {{ data.agent.lastName }}</td>
                            <td>{{ data.shifts|length }}</td>
                            <td>{{ data.hours_day|number_format(1) }}h</td>
                            <td>{{ data.hours_night|number_format(1) }}h</td>
                            <td><strong>{{ data.total_hours|number_format(1) }}h</strong></td>
                            <td><strong>{{ agentAmount|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</strong></td>
                        </tr>
                    {% else %}
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="6" style="text-align: center; color: #64748b;">Aucune intervention sur cette période</td>
                        </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Totals -->
        <div class="totals-section">
            <div class="totals-spacer">
                <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 10px;">
                    <strong>Taux horaires appliqués:</strong><br>
                    Heures de jour: {{ hourlyRateDay|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €/h<br>
                    Heures de nuit: {{ hourlyRateNight|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €/h
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="totals-box">
                <div class="total-row">
                    <span class="total-label">Sous-total HT</span>
                    <span class="total-value">{{ subtotal|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</span>
                </div>
                <div class="total-row">
                    <span class="total-label">TVA (20%)</span>
                    <span class="total-value">{{ (subtotal * 0.20)|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</span>
                </div>
                <div class="grand-total">
                    <div class="total-row" style="border: none; padding: 0;">
                        <span class="total-label">TOTAL TTC</span>
                        <span class="total-value">{{ (subtotal * 1.20)|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p class="footer-note">
                <strong>Conditions de paiement:</strong> Paiement à 30 jours fin de mois<br>
                En cas de retard de paiement, des pénalités de 3 fois le taux d'intérêt légal seront appliquées.
            </p>
            <p>
                Phoenix Security SARL - SIRET: 123 456 789 00012 - TVA: FR12345678901<br>
                Document généré le {{ 'now'|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }}
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
